<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Special Delivery for Sharon</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff5f5;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        h1 { color: #ff4d6d; }
        p { color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
        .buttons {
            margin-top: 25px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }
        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-yes { background-color: #ff4d6d; color: white; }
        .btn-no { background-color: #ccc; color: white; }
        .btn-yes:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
        #response-message {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff4d6d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Halo Sharon! 🌸</h1>
    <p>Makanannya sudah sampai belum nih?</p>
    
    <div class="buttons" id="button-group">
        <button class="btn-yes" onclick="showSurprise()">Sudah Diterima</button>
        <button class="btn-no" onclick="notYet()">Belum Diterima</button>
    </div>

    <div id="response-message">
        <p>Selamat menikmati yaa Sharon, <br> 
        happy teruss, semanggat yaa hari ini.. Gbuu! ✨</p>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    function showSurprise() {
        document.getElementById('button-group').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('response-message').style.display = 'block';
    }

    function notYet() {
        alert("Sabar yaa, mungkin abangnya lagi di jalan. Cek berkala ya Sharon! 😊");
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
